<div id="Idea_2813"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2813-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2813">Restore voting rights for convicted felons&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/0-4049">jmdean</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">9 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">It is the fundamental right of every American citizen to vote.  This right should be accorded to every American citizen, whether they are a convicted felon or not.</div>
