<a href="/akira/dtd/2799-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2799">Make sure there are participatory processes for the truly disenfranchised&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/0-4049">marcella</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">9 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">The homeless, prisoners, children, adults with literacy and/or English as a Second Language: These are just a few of the groups that do not have easy access to a participatory system such as this one. Create targeted ways and means for these groups to participate and have a voice.</div>
